John Hargreaves (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Hargreaves_(actor) 0 John William Hargreaves (28 November 1945 – 8 January 1996) was an Australian actor. He won three Australian Film Institute Awards and was nominated six times. John_William_Hargreaves ( 28_November_1945 – 8_January_1996 ) was an_Australian_actor .
